text: Elytracanthina propinqua is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Lane in 1959. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Elytracanthina propinqua. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1959
